{"tid":2173189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林太：專家食屎啦！","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T13:21:42.000Z","uid":11454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"271040b5146432c41ad588bca64f9e4510db1e5c","tid":2173189,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171226/large/1514295329_8a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171226%2Flarge%2F1514295329_8a36.jpg&h=08216203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街頭智慧勝專家，嘉湖山莊林太2016年一句叫樓市專家食屎，成為網絡紅人，更是不少網民心目中的「女神」。林太的出現，同時亦令到一班唱淡樓市的專家無地自容。<br />\n<br />\n2016年1月6日，蘋果記者直擊天水圍嘉湖山莊，當時區內業主林太表示，半個月前阿仔買入樂湖居兩房單位，成交價330萬元。被問到市場不少專家指樓價跌一成，林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n林太發表「專家食屎」論當日，嘉湖山莊的平均呎價只是約6,800元，兩房單位300萬元有交易。但在林太發表「專家食屎」快兩周年，現時嘉湖山平均呎價已升至近9,500元，升幅高達四成，兩房單位平均造價約440萬元。林太阿囝單位已升值逾百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171226/57629927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F57629927&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXe9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=a1a679f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F57629927&h=0cebe295\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171226/57629927</a>"},{"pid":"c26e4e28b835330aae031e09b1b015d80ef7b888","tid":2173189,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b5e1857c98e400ec421cae35a0689e31eeb3ee","tid":2173189,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"根本好多所謂專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bc518f85d93426ad6c22ad799aa271b4e01145","tid":2173189,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:00:44.000Z","msg":"林太<del>:專家</del>食屎啦！"},{"pid":"1deab382b2a84d800b6c38c4d53f7aa4965187fa","tid":2173189,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"街頭智慧勝專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}